  "signal_description": "The query retrieves the average cycle time, average invoice payment time, and PO plant from the 'defaultview-124' table. It calculates the average cycle time by subtracting the last end time from the first end time. It also calculates the average invoice payment time by subtracting the last end time of the 'Clear Invoice' event from the first end time of the 'Record Invoice Receipt' and 'Create FI Invoice' events. Additionally, it sums the 'Last FI Invoice Item Gross Amount Local Curr.' column and renames it as 'Invoice Amount (INR)'. Finally, it orders the results by the third column in descending order."
